    <description>PAP adherence will be measured from the PAP unit (which monitors nightly hours of use and records this data; this is the standard of care clinical practice approach used currently by health care providers to monitor PAP use) and will be reported as hours of use per night on average across the 30 day period (hours of use per night is the most commonly used criteria for adherence).</description>
